Entities.Name: CredentialTracker
Entities.Description: Tracker to enable check-in/check-out of non shareable application credentials. All bots will check out credentials from this table by marking them "IN USE" and check in credentials by marking them "FREE". Only after a credential has been checked out, the bot will invoke GetCredentialFromVault automation from UP_Lib_Connector_HashiCorpVault to get password.
